songs.title: Come When You Call Me America
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
A-M-E-R-I-C-A
Ah-ah-ay

[Chorus]
Come when you call me
Come when you call me

[Verse 1]
Just like you wanna know why
Just like you said so, night
I can do whatever I want
You can do whatever you
It's just like I always wanted
Just like I always knew

[Pre-Chorus]
Riding my time
Have a night life
Have a night life
Head to head
Gun to gun
Now we're gonna
Have some fun
(Hey-ah)

[Chorus]
Come when you call me
Come when you call me

[Verse 2]
This what I wanna know why
Just like you said so, night
(Hey-ah)

[Pre-Chorus - Variation]
Riding my time
Have a night life (have a night life)
I know what you
Been looking for
I think I got
All that and more
I think I know
What you been trying
Saying "everybody wants a little time"

[Chorus - Variation]
Come when you call me
Come when you
(A-M-E-R-I-C-A)

[Verse 3]
Just like you wanna know why
Just like you said so, night
(A-M-E-R-I-C-A)
I can do whatever I want
You can do whatever you
This is like I always wanted
Just like I always knew
(Tell me a story, daddy)

[Chorus - Variation]
Come when you call me
Come when you
(A-M-E-R-I-C-A)

[Bridge]
You can say whatever
You gonna say about me
(A-M-E-R-I-C-A)
You can say whatever
You gonna say about me
(A-M-E-R-I-C-A)
You can say whatever
You gonna say about me
(I like you, I like)
(A-M-E-R-I-C-A)

[Outro]
Hey-ah, ooh
Hey-ah, ooh
Stay in your room
Get in your bed
Maybe they can get me
Inside your head
(A-M-E-R-I-C-A)
Tell me a story, daddy
